          {{> partials/item title="Automation" subtitle=(split 'Continuous compliance and drift remediation for an estate of 10000+ machines.;SCM Gatekeeping integrated with ChatOps.') }}

          {{> partials/item title="CI/CD" subtitle=(split 'Jenkins and Travis are my stomping grounds. Check out the <a href="#reverie">Reverie</a> PRs for a sneak peek of the standards I set myself.') }}

